  "text": "One other reason for low resolution is that the measurement sensitivity decreases drastically with the increasing distance from the electrodes. Ts et al. [CITATION_1] proposed an EIT system with a novel electrode configuration to address this limitation. In this system, two pairs of driving electrodes attached on four sides of the surface of the body, and an array of voltage sensing electrodes are placed along the surface as shown in Fig. 7 .",
